speaker.name: Laís Carvalho
speaker.biography: Developer Advocate, Laís had led events in tech communities to promote the use and diminish the entry barrier to the Python programming language. Board member of Python Ireland, Member of the EuroPython Society and PyLadies Dublin, she has a habit of making fun of everything.
